<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire are the major disturbances. Plants are not resistant to fires, though they may sprout easily after disturbance. Plants may increase after fire, though average plant size is reduced in the short-term.</div>
